Outro 1
--------------------------------------------------
As you touch the hologram, your mind is overwhelmed by knowledge. This moment is the culmination of many years of search.
What seemed to be a mystery is clear to you now. You searched for an alien species but you found so much more. 


The theory in 'Evolution of Information' was right. The universe is alive. 
It is a self-aware being that has created itself via loop holes in physical laws. 
Its ultimate target - self-understanding.
It has developed through the ages and explored itself by creating intelligent organisms with observation and analysis capabilities.